en-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>哈尔西还以她新专辑的主打歌拉开了演出的序幕，这是有史以来第一次现场演奏。这张专辑在演出前不到一周发行，这是她的第五张录音室唱片，也是自 2021 年的《<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/halsey-if-i-cant-have-love-i-want-power-review-3030014">如果我不能拥有爱，我想要力量</a>》以来的第一张专辑。</p><h2><strong>哈尔西在洛杉矶的亚马逊音乐现场演奏：</strong> </h2><ol><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="641" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1.&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><strong>伟大的模仿者</strong></li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="641" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1.&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><strong>不擅长爱情</strong></li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="641" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1.&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><strong>惊恐发作</strong></li><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="" data-listid="641" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0